n\n---\n\n#### 8. Final statement  \n\n> \u201cAlice wins for every \\(\\lambda>0\\); for \\(\\lambda=0\\) the game never terminates; Bazza never has a winning strategy.\u201d\n\n*Consistent* with the preceding rigorous analysis.\n\n---\n\n### Overall Assessment\nAll lemmas, existence arguments, and the construction of Alice\u2019s winning strategy are rigorously justified. No logical fallacies, calculation errors, or unjustified steps are present. Consequently, the solution is correct."
